data.description: Elegantly nestled atop a commanding hill, this residence offers an enchanting panorama of the surrounding landscape. Marvel at the breathtaking sunsets that grace the horizon, a daily spectacle from the comfort of your own abode. The expansive backyard, thoughtfully enclosed, invites you to host delightful gatherings and revel in the tranquil outdoors.    Step inside, and you'll discover an inviting open floor plan that effortlessly melds spaces, fostering a sense of airiness and interconnectedness. With four spacious bedrooms, there's room for everyone to unwind, and a dedicated office space is a sanctuary for remote work or creative endeavors.    Nestled on a serene, tree-lined street, this idyllic location is tailor-made for your growing family, offering both respite and proximity to essential amenities. Your dream home awaits.    Live like you’re on vacation! Located in the Lago Vista POA, giving you nine waterfront parks, up to 4 boat, ramps, basketball courts, tennis courts, pickle ball courts, fitness centers, golf course, frisbee golf courses, fishing, unlimited lake access and endless fun!!! making this the best area in all of Austin Metro.
